name: Dakota Skye
description:
Dakota Skye

She left us too soon...for reals this time. She led a difficult and troubled life that ended way too soon, but not before she was able to share her, um, gifts with the world. Godspeed, sweet child.

From a run of 5000 steps I pulled the 3400 step sample from and she looks spectacuar. I hope you like her!

Built on v1.5, she looks best on all of the nicer Models available here.

NOTE: You will want to specify "short hair" since she will occasionally gen with long hair and it'sjust not the same, you know?

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
